headline: Aflac (NYSE:AFL) Misses Q2 Sales Targets
summary: Supplemental insurance provider Aflac (NYSE:AFL) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, with sales falling 5.1% year on year to $4.16 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.11 per share was 34.9% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
